{"tid":845273,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣訓練狗仔去廁所？","createTime":"2018-10-02T13:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T09:59:40.000Z","uid":206873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31e44a331377d775aa5dd5b02a2be041fe1c46e9","tid":845273,"uid":206873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:50:49.000Z","msg":"隻狗女成日都係廳中間\u0016\u0016屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0505edd8dd73d617de1790c51c32e30c5a4b2638","tid":845273,"uid":38318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:54:51.000Z","msg":"你試範一次先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea25af2a084dd2d986d296d0ad0a3e9b5a537c90","tid":845273,"uid":146063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:13:58.000Z","msg":"鬧9佢"},{"pid":"7f2a9f26f0430a10241f655fc5d87fb90b4583ae","tid":845273,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:10:45.000Z","msg":"0？"},{"pid":"a5c5e5ff53d7993850e4e878aa2540c56b5e737e","tid":845273,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"上淘寶買廁板送尿味噴霧<br />\n噴完識定點屙屎屙尿<br />\n我隻狗都係用佢<br />\n唔醒一個月內都識<br />\n醒就幾日"},{"pid":"89e9a5a4357f99b5f6f3a3a7da04069ebe214eac","tid":845273,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"首先你要觀察咗佢嘅行為模式先<br />\n你感覺到佢想屙 你就帶佢去你想佢屙嘅位置<br />\n佢屙咗之後 你獎勵一小粒零食比佢<br />\n並以高八度讚佢 狗仔與生俱來就感覺高音係開心 低音似啲狗媽發惡嘅嗚嗚聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之佢屙一次 你就要獎同讚一次<br />\n佢屙錯 你唔好鬧 唔出聲清潔咗佢就得<br />\n久而久之 佢會為咗獎勵去啱嘅位置<br />\n當然狗仔越細 教得越易<br />\n年齡一大就好難教 要花多啲時間<br />\n<br />\n唔建議買樓上啲噴霧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之前咩噴霧都試過<br />\n呢啲真係因狗而異 用心教佢仲好"}]}